@startuml
title UC11 - Chatbot Screen Flow
start
:User opens chatbot widget;
if (Logged in?) then (yes)
  :Enter question;
  if (Question allowed and within limits?) then (yes)
    :Send question with safe context;
    :Show AI response;
  else (no)
    :Show validation/rate-limit/read-only error;
  endif
else (no)
  :Prompt login;
endif
stop
@enduml
